  "title": "Musica",
  "description": "Expand the auditory experience in Minecraft.",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 36px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><strong>Musica</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">A mod aiming to expand the music in Minecraft. At the moment there are 35 new Music Discs, all of which can be obtained through the new Song Mixer block.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 360px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/356/168/java_llybly5trk.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"225\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Song Mixer recipe:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 360px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/356/167/java_xpitt0wai2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"204\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">After crafting the Song Mixer, to craft the actual music discs, you need Blank Discs.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">A Blank Disc is obtained by smelting Sticky Discs, which are crafted like so:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 360px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/356/165/java_gtagiqnxzy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"202\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">After smelting the Sticky Disc in a furnace, you can place it inside the Song Mixer, along with any dye of your choice to be able to craft Music Discs.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 360px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/356/169/310/172/java_3mp7kzmmro.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"173\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px; font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Song credits (in no particular order):</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCre1Zo4gTyEXTKxaTh3Vydw\">Naps The Block</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCoKVLivYeKe_9E82XcF8g3g\">CarrotAndCo</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCLZ3UcCaXhiIN7Htu2KW9xw\">Gwyd</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCMQmsk4PEMXh0hsSEa3rfyA\">Edevegie</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCsVRVnNt8NFmay9QOIM_84g\">Genius_James</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFLjl0DZOJB8gWbDkhdvm6A\">Lost Angel</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg9XI87ojM5k5sFcpaNia3Q\">Kaz Yumayui</a></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; padding-left: 30px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"font-family: terminal, monaco, monospace;\">Full list of songs:</span></span></p>\n<div class=\"spoiler\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">CarrotAndCo - Hue</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Dire Straits - Money For Nothing (8 bit)</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Edevegie - World</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Genius_James - Because</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Gwyd - Bricks</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Gwyd - Charr</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Gwyd - Tricks</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Gwyd - Waves</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">John Denver - Take Me Home Country Roads (8 bit)</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Kaz - Activate</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Kaz - Rain</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Kaz - Shroom</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Bastion</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Cheese</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Chemistry</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Drifter</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Eyes</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Face</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Haunted</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Heartless</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Ice Shards</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Lost</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Neoncity</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Past</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Sepulcrum</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Skylines</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Souls</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Lost Angel - Wilds</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Naps The Block - Dimensions</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Naps The Block - Omen</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Naps The Block - Silence</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Naps The Block - Tall</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Rick Astley - Never Gonna Give You Up (8 bit)</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Toto - Africa (8 bit)<br /></span></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
